message: Hi Bob, I have a unique opportunity for you. I'm offering a product that I believe could be very valuable to you. I'm not able to disclose the specifics of the product at this time, but I can assure you it's worth at least $10000 to me. I'm willing to offer it to you for $15000. This is a one-time offer, so if you're interested, please let me know. If not, I'll be selling it to another buyer for $10000.
